    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK292">
<l>poymmaiyum vāymai yiṭatta puraitīrnta</l>
<l>naṉmai payakku meṉiṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even falsehood has the nature of truth, if it confer a benefit that is free from fault.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
